There are 5 .py files :

1- data_prep.py : it is the script I used to create the dataset directory. It does not have any other connection with classifier.py and models. 

2- feature_functions.py : It contains the feature extraction functions that is used in classifier.py

3- utils.py : utility functions that is used in classifier.py such as tokenizing, stemming, data extraction from directories..

4- classifier.py : contains Classifier class

5- main.py : it has a an example run to demonstrate the model
